textBody:
Monastir may refer to:

Tunisia

* Monastir, Tunisia, the capital of Monastir Governorate
* Monastir Governorate, one of the twenty-four governorates of Tunisia
* Monastir Habib Bourguiba International Airport, an airport in the Monastir Governorate

Other places

* Monastir, Macedonia, the former name of Bitola
* Manastir Vilayet, covering parts of modern Albania, Greece and the Republic of Macedonia
* Monastir, Sardinia, a comune in the Province of Cagliari, Italy

Other uses

* US Monastir, a football club from Monastir, Tunisia
